POD2-IT-Getopt-Long version 1.02
================================

POD2::IT::Getopt::Long - Italian translation of Getopt::Long
Perl module.

See http://pod2it.sourceforge.net for more details about the 
Italian Perldoc Translation Project.

CHANGES FROM PREVIOUS VERSION

	+ Fixed typos
	
See 'Changes' file in this distribution for complete history revision.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module doesn't require other modules and libraries.

